        return TokenManager(/* dependencies */)
    }
}
```

3. **Check the Hilt setup**

Make sure that Hilt is properly set up in your project. You should have the `@HiltAndroidApp` annotation in your Application class, and the `kaptHilt` plugin should be applied in your app-level `build.gradle` file.

